tween fingers and toes in ablution","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"December 1, 2017","format":false,"excerpt":"Ibn Abbas reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cWhen you perform ablution, run your fingers between the fingers on your hands and your toes.\u201d Source: Sunan al-Tirmidhi\u0304 39 Grade: Sahih (authentic) according to Al-Albani \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u0627\u0628\u0652\u0646\u0650 \u0639\u064e\u0628\u0651\u064e\u0627\u0633\u064d \u0623\u064e\u0646\u0651\u064e \u0631\u064e\u0633\u064f\u0648\u0644\u064e \u0627\u0644\u0644\u0651\u064e\u0647\u0650 \u0635\u064e\u0644\u0651\u064e\u0649 \u0627\u0644\u0644\u0651\u064e\u0647\u064f \u0639\u064e\u0644\u064e\u064a\u0652\u0647\u0650 \u0648\u064e\u0633\u064e\u0644\u0651\u064e\u0645\u064e\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/wisdom-al-hikmah\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":25423,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2017\/11\/13\/no-wudu-wajib-touch-private\/","url_meta":{"origin":10670,"position":4},"title":"Hadith on Wudu: No renewal of ablution after touching private parts","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"November 13, 2017","format":false,"excerpt":"Talq ibn 'Ali reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, was asked about touching the private area and he said, \u201cIs it not but a piece of flesh, or a part of you?\" Al-Tirmidhi said, \u201cIt has been narrated from more than one of the companions\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/wisdom-al-hikmah\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"cl